{"tid":1485003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[得罪講句]818絕對唔係和理非, 只係警察唔清你場","createTime":"2019-08-18T15:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T15:32:35.000Z","uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d80db60e05069cdbb1a56dec47f0ac1555e3f9fb","tid":1485003,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:24:45.000Z","msg":"咩818和理非共識, 根本只係和理非圍爐打飛機<br />\n從來和理非同勇武都係兩個圈子, 並無集體共識可言<br />\n<br />\n818根本唔係和理非, 只係警察唔清你場"},{"pid":"de109cd4edc613144a753b7a5aca729ea6f5e5c1","tid":1485003,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:25:22.000Z","msg":"前線唔駛叫人走，你要走左先，人少左就無留低理由<br />\n<br />\n每位巴絲麻煩各發一個貼， 要連登頭版都係依個caption"},{"pid":"9f8e8a384720143375e7f0cd9e14cedbc744c414","tid":1485003,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"<strong>叫左唔好屌鬼<br />\n<br />\n大家係咪學唔識<br />\n<br />\n又變成自己人打自己人啦！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200954406608272/posts/2376648385705519/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200954406608272%2Fposts%2F2376648385705519%2F&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=f74257bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200954406608272/posts/2376648385705519/</a><br />\n<br />\n示威者互射鐳射光起爭執<br />\n白衣男頭破血流<br />\n<br />\n【即時】(23:24) 剛才於金鐘夏愨道有示威者發生衝突，一名白衣男子被大批民眾包圍，頭破血流，需要接受急救。<br />\n<br />\n白衣男子向記者表示自己不是警察，又稱受傷原因是意外跌倒，要求記者不要再追問，並否認自己曾叉別人頸。<br />\n<br />\n但同場有示威者承認，剛才於天橋上為了向朋友展示所處位置，向橋下照射鐳射光，但照到了另一群示威者，以致發生爭執，為此致歉。<br />\n<br />\n【不斷更新】8.18民陣維園「流水式」集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YY2A0F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YY2A0F&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=ead9fa59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YY2A0F</a><br />\n<br />\n金鐘現場直播：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KEamnG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KEamnG&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=35e8572d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KEamnG</a><br />\n<br />\n#獨媒報導<br />\n追蹤最新消息：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=2aeb45f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\n報導有價，請月捐支持<br />\n<a href=\"http://inmediahk.net/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cd8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=94835da4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&h=5011d3a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">inmediahk.net/donate</a>"}]}